    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">保卫你的盆地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>TDS Tower Defense Strategy</strong> 是以塔防、实时策略为核心的混合体。建造、防御并在逼近的潮汐中生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/f223137bcd7ba6220f0bd149b3867467.avif?t=1768226890\" width=590 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/10757c830b79238687953b959c4eb701.poster.avif?t=1768226890\" width=692 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/10757c830b79238687953b959c4eb701.webm?t=1768226890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/10757c830b79238687953b959c4eb701.mp4?t=1768226890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/88a3ce513481676ae176897ec5229caa.webp?t=1768226890\" width=590 height=10 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>控制船只，它们是你的灵魂</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">容器既是一个单元又是一座塔。控制他们采矿、战斗并建立防御。每艘船都配有自己的一套极其独特的塔楼来提供帮助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>塔楼和单元。简单又复杂。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">通过一系列极其丰富且相互配合的升级来扩展您的防御。协同作用，您可以采用多种组合和策略来增强防御。塔楼可以相互进化，船只也可以。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/88a3ce513481676ae176897ec5229caa.webp?t=1768226890\" width=590 height=10 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/47014487c7f467107b5e0df544091cdd.poster.avif?t=1768226890\" width=590 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/47014487c7f467107b5e0df544091cdd.webm?t=1768226890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/47014487c7f467107b5e0df544091cdd.mp4?t=1768226890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/88a3ce513481676ae176897ec5229caa.webp?t=1768226890\" width=590 height=10 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>智力和力量。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">安置很重要；你可以靠力量生存，但你也可以靠智慧生存。您的行为在很多方面都很重要。创建一个超强大的单塔，创建一个牢不可破的墙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>TDS 和朋友一起更好！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">最多可使用 4 艘战舰并肩作战！和朋友一起玩有更多的组合和策略 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/88a3ce513481676ae176897ec5229caa.webp?t=1768226890\" width=590 height=10 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/ba859d43321aeff0972e53b0368732be.poster.avif?t=1768226890\" width=584 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/ba859d43321aeff0972e53b0368732be.webm?t=1768226890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/ba859d43321aeff0972e53b0368732be.mp4?t=1768226890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/88a3ce513481676ae176897ec5229caa.webp?t=1768226890\" width=590 height=10 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">游戏很有挑战性。这可能真的很难，也很容易。玩得开心！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">加入我们的 Discord</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">GOOGLE &lt;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/d9c99a3430443e26054f718c833b91d3.avif?t=1768226890\" width=590 height=64 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/25b82ffc66408c2b9865b64a6cb61530.apng?t=1768226890\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392280/extras/25b82ffc66408c2b9865b64a6cb61530.poster.avif?t=1768226890\" class=\"bb_img\" width=590 height=32 /></picture></span></p>",
